data.description: BEAUTIFUL & SPACIOUS HOME WITH 3-CAR GARAGE!! OPEN LAYOUT GIVES THIS HOME A SPACIOUS FEEL. KITCHEN WITH WHITE CABINETS, GRANITE COUNTER TOPS, SS APPLIANCES & PANTRY, NEW REFRIGERATOR & DISHWASHER. MASTER BDRM WITH HIGH CEILINGS, BALCONY W/ GREAT MOUNTAIN VIEW & WALK-IN CLOSET W/ CUSTOM ORGANIZER. MASTER BATH WITH DUAL SINK VANITY, SEPARATE TUB & SHOWER. 4TH GUEST BDRM UPSTAIRS IS EXTRA LARGE & WITH HIGH CEILINGS, IT CAN BE USED AS GAME & THEATER ROOM. A/C & FURNACE (2 UNTS) WERE REPLACED IN 2021, VERY ENERGY EFFICIENT.  LOW MAINTENANCE BACKYARD: COVERED PATIO W/ CEILING FANS, PAVERS & SYNTHETIC GRASS. COMMUNITY IS NEXT TO GILCREASE NATURE SANCTUARY & FLOYD LAMB PARK. . CLOSE TO SHOPPING, DINING & EASY ACCESS TO FREEWAYS. BUYER CAN ASSUME THE EXISTING LOAN (VA) IF BUYER IS QUALIFIED.  THE INTEREST RATE IS 2.25%.
